<i>noun</i>: 제련소 [제ː련소] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>제련소 [제ː련소]</dt><br>
<dd>refinery</dd><br>
<dd>광석을 용광로에 넣고 녹여서 금속을 뽑아내어 불순물을 없애고 순수하게 만드는 곳.</dd><br>
<dd>A place where metal is extracted from ores melted in a blast furnace before impurities are removed to ensure the metal's purity.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>